Bind 9
======

Bind howto (Debian/Ubuntu):
	https://wiki.debian.org/Bind9


Fast configuration (ex: mydomain.local):
	Software setup:
		 $ apt-get install bind9 # bind9-doc
		 $ sudo mkdir /var/log/named
		 $ sudo chown bind:bind /var/log/named
		 $ sudo chmod 755 /var/log/named
	Configuration files:
		/etc/bind/named.conf.local
			| zone "mydomain.local" {
			|     type master;
			|     
	Automated (Script):
		https://github.com/bitifet/bashLib/blob/master/bindSetup.sh



